Acceptance Criteria
- Loader handles API success and failure gracefully with fallback data.
- All four API queries execute in parallel via `Promise.all`.
- Summary metrics accurately reflect current state (open alerts, active incidents, etc.).
- Tabs switch correctly between Metrics, Alerts, Incidents, and Log Forwarders.
- Status badges display with correct colors based on severity/status.
- Metric values formatted correctly (percentages, units, etc.).
- Date formatting uses `Intl.DateTimeFormat` consistently.
- Empty states handle gracefully when no records in a category.

